          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/91847.Nizami_Ganjavi"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1227023895p3/91847.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
